<h2 id="raspberry-pi">Raspberry Pi</h2>
<p>Raspberry Pi provides a Linux environment which is equivalent to a traditional VPS. A regular server stack can be built using Apache or Nginx, with PHP, Python, MariaDB, MongoDB or any other services needed.</p>
